title: Ghatak / Lethal
subTitle: For his father's treatment, Kashi and his father move into a colony on the outskirts of Mumbai. But when Kashi sees a local gangster terrorise the colony, he decides to strike back.

title: Illaka
subTitle: Two brothers grow up and end up choosing career paths that are polar opposites, one becomes a smuggler and the other a police officer.

title: Mera Faisla
subTitle: Raj wishes to marry Rati but faces humiliation from her father due to the stigma associated with his lineage. Soon, he decides to join the police force to restore his family's honour.

title: Saajan Ki Saheli
subTitle: Kunti abandons her baby in order to lead a lavish life and marries a rich man. Years later, she realises that her husband is indulging in an affair and is shocked to find out the truth about the girl.

title: Majaal
subTitle: Vijay Kumar, an orphan, is brought up by an advocate. While he falls in love with his daughter and marries her, he struggles to cope with the humiliation he faces from her family.

title: Eena Meena Deeka
subTitle: A bank robbery mix-up sets the scene for a crackbrained cat-and-mouse game involving a troubled culprit, a fresh-out-of-jail customer and a policeman's feisty daughter.

title: Kyon Ki
subTitle: In the chaotic environment of a faraway psychiatric hospital, love blossoms between a closed-off doctor and a rebellious patient with a troubled past.

title: Prem
subTitle: Sanjay gets visions and sees his past life where his name was Shantanu. His life turns upside down when, on a visit to a village, he meets Sonia, who resembles Lachi from his visions.

title: Taal
subTitle: A businessman's budding romance with an aspiring singer faces challenges as he departs, leaving her suave manager to step in and complicate their relationship.

title: Taal

title: Chori Mera Kaam
subTitle: Chori Mera Kaam

title: 15th August
subTitle: Nagpal kills Chaudhry and his son, Ram, a military officer. Chaudhry's second son, Vikram, vows to destroy Nagpal who is all set to become the Chief Minister on the upcoming Indian Independence Day.

title: Shiva Shakti
subTitle: Shiva forms a close friendship with Shakti when he comes to the city to earn money for his sister Kusum's wedding. However, he later vows to kill Shakti when Kusum becomes pregnant with his child.

title: Devta
subTitle: An ordinary taxi driver becomes part of a notorious gang through a twist of fate and takes on the role of a terrifying assassin.

title: No Entry
subTitle: A gorgeous club dancer's ill-timed rendezvous opens up a Pandora's box of lies, absurdities and misunderstandings in the lives of three quirky couples.

title: Loha
subTitle: After a bid to arrest Sher Singh fails, officer Dayal is crippled and his partner Amar's career is sabotaged. When Amar gets another chance to nab Sher Singh, he hires two crooks for the job.

title: Naseeb
subTitle: The lives of friends Namdev, Raghu, Damu and Jaggi take a turn for the worse when they win a lottery. Raghu and Damu murder Jaggi and frame Namdev who later returns to seek revenge.

title: Josh
subTitle: Set in Vasco, Goa, Max and Prakash are young men who lead two rival groups. Their feud becomes worse when Prakash's brother, Rahul, falls in love with Shirley, Max's twin sister.

title: Josh
subTitle: Set in Vasco, Goa, Max and Prakash are young men who lead two rival groups. Their feud becomes worse when Prakash's brother, Rahul, falls in love with Shirley, Max's twin sister.

title: Azad Desh Ka Andha Kanoon
subTitle: An honest policemen is forced to choose between duty and family when his brother is caught as part of a gang producing blue-films. He must also protect a witness whose life is threatened.

title: Kaun Kare Kurbanie
subTitle: Arjun Singh, a police inspector, lives peacefully with his family in Mumbai, until an alarming case of harassment and murder turns his life upside down.

title: Jaan Se Pyaara
subTitle: Inspector Jai balances working as a cop with taking care of his mother and a brother with developmental disabilities. But when he arrests a local don, he starts to fear for his family's safety.

title: 16 December
subTitle: Four IRS officers race against the clock to disarm the nuclear bomb planted by a rebel Pakistani terrorist in New Delhi.

title: Wafadaar
subTitle: Chanda's parents disapprove of her boyfriend Ranga and want her to marry Prasad. Ranga is accused of having an affair with Sita.

title: Daanveer
subTitle: After the death of his parents, Vijay becomes a car driver to support his family. His hardships increase when his sister's marriage falls through.

title: B4U Kadak
subTitle: A gangster's driver takes the blame for an accident, leaving his family alone. He seeks revenge when he finds out what happened to them while he was gone.

title: China Gate
subTitle: Colonel Puri requests his former fellow army officers court-martialed in disgrace to redeem themselves by rescuing a village from Jageera, an evil bandit.
